{"tid":403811,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"老人家點解有關愛座唔坐走去坐普通座位","createTime":"2017-09-17T13:29:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T13:57:54.000Z","uid":106523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c2e1cf2a48d25c4f21533b2c3576ecd5f1d5004","tid":403811,"uid":106523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T13:29:03.000Z","msg":"收工搭地鐵<br />\n一上車<br />\n見到成堆老人家唔坐關愛座 坐曬普通座位<br />\n明明關愛座就空既<br />\n周圍其他人又無人坐落去<br />\n咁我唔理啦 返完通宵更眼訓 照坐關愛座啦<br />\n兩個站唔夠就有老人家企係面前<br />\n屌咁又唯有讓位<br />\n<br />\n其實如果d老人家肯自己fill曬d關愛座先<br />\n咁我就唔洗企足十鳩幾個站<br />\n專登整比你用又唔用<br />\n想點撚樣呢？"},{"pid":"7df30cbfc88fddc889457b8875b6681fec088003","tid":403811,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T13:35:00.000Z","msg":"On9 讓座比廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce1c6bfa56e5b6500f0f395a74a892003b871b8","tid":403811,"uid":8951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T13:54:31.000Z","msg":"廢老夠團結"},{"pid":"3b1ad26fb46cf6d0fc074bc532c5ad1a37c429c9","tid":403811,"uid":27729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T13:57:54.000Z","msg":"係到講有用咩<br />\n廢老都唔會上連登"}]}